eas_text: A CIVIL AUTHORITY HAS ISSUED A CHILD ABDUCTION EMERGENCY FOR THE FOLLOWING COUNTIES/AREAS: Austin; Bastrop; Bell; Blanco; Brazos; Burleson; Burnet; Caldwell; Colorado; Coryell; Falls; Fayette; Gillespie; Hays; Kendall; Kerr; Kimble; Lampasas; Lee; Llano; McCulloch; McLennan; Mason; Milam; Mills; Robertson; San Saba; Travis; Washington; Williamson, TX; AT 10:25 PM ON NOV 04, 2025 EFFECTIVE UNTIL 10:40 PM. MESSAGE FROM WSLF/CAP.
extra_text: Local AMBER Alert: Abducted Child from Austin, Texas. Missing child is Armani Woods, 50 day old black male. Suspect is Kayla Washington, 32 year old black female, last seen wearing a dark navy blue shirt and black sweat pants. Call Austin Police Department with information. If seen call 9 1 1.
